Betty Francisco https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Betty_Francisco 0 Betty Francisco (September 26, 1900 – November 25, 1950), born Elizabeth Barton in Little Rock, Arkansas, was an American silent-film actor, appearing in films of many genres primarily in supporting roles.
